brewery.brewery_description: Carrig Brewing Company is an independent, family owned business, located in Drumshanbo, Co. Leitrim and is set in the Old Laird Jam Factory, although now producing an exciting range of Craft Beers for the Domestic and International markets, the location of the Brewery is steeped in Irish Tradition and is the first Brewery in over 150 years to be brewing in County Leitrim.

beer.beer_description: Rowers Red Ale is a celebration of malts that has a fruity and aromatic finish. Pouring to a ruby red colour, we use a generous blend of sweet malts to give Rowers its distinctive toffee nose. The hops used, balance the sweetness with lingering moderately bitter fruit flavours. Enjoyed best at 10°C.
